Review Text: Madhuri is an absolute delight to work with. My Cake was truly elegant and delicious. I cannot recommend a cake high enough. Would highly recommend her. 😊

This is our first order with madhuri & v are very satisfied. She is friendly. The red velvet cup cakes tastes yumm & the customization was as required. Will definitely recommend to my friends.thanks a lot madhuri once again 👍👍👍great job
My friends got my bday cake from here and it was very Yummy. I loved the way it was decorated with all my fav things.... Loved it... Thank you so much for making my day special..
We ordered a customized cake it looked so amazing! The taste was very good! Its a very creative idea! The detailing which was done is very good. Thank you so much for the delicious cake.

For my husband’s birthday this year I didn’t wanted to just order some cake and was scanning facebook. Interestingly came across Doughicious page and thought of trying the cupcakes by customizing. I contacted Madhuri and provide her all the information, but was amazed when i saw the picture of the cupcakes. My husband was surprised though, he had a thought that customize cakes and cupcakes doesn’t taste good. After having his first bite, he was like where is this place that you order these. I am surely going to order stuffs from here.

Been to many places but dis is da first time m writing review. Had a wonderful experience with “DOUGHICIOUS”.  Ordered customized rich chocolate cake and it was really perfect in design, taste😋😋 and everything that a perfect cake need to be👌🏻.  Ms. Madhuri u made it awesome👏🏻👏🏻. Everyone in da party just loved it,  Will surely order again.  Highly satisfied and highly recommended😊

Cakes from this shop are more just delicacies!! They make memories! The detailing which is done is really impressive! The taste is very good, the cream is so light and overall a big 5/5 for the cake !!
Another wonderful aspect of it is the designs.
Thanks for making my Birthday more special!

I had an amazing experience with doughicious. There cakes are absolutely wonderful . I ordered a small chocolate truffle cake and was highly satisfied. Everyone loved the cake. Absolutely soft and not like those watery cakes.the frosting was yum. And the decoration on the cake was spot on. I just asked for a simple truffle cake and gave the baker Madhuri one simple quote to write on the cake. I did not give any instructions about the decoration but the end result was so beautiful. Highly recommended.
Ordered cake just one day before, but delivered with Gr8 quality. Liked the way the followup and punctuality. So many theme cakes and options are available
We orderd customized rich chocolate cake and it was great! Thank you for the perfect cake in such a short notice! Loved the taste! 😍 Will surely visit again 😊

Thank you so much for the delicious Velvet cake.
The cake looked amazing to eat and tasted even better. Keep the good work going. Will surely visit back.

We Ordered The Red Velvet Cake For My Friends Birthday..
Perfect Red Velvet Inside Covered With Lots Of Chocolate Icing And KitKat Around..
Loveeeed The Combination Of Chocolate And Red Velvet.. ❤️
And Madhuri Was Very Sweet ..
Highly Recommend This Place For Some Good Cakes..
Gonna Order Soon Again !

we ordered custom cupcakes from here.
in such a short notice , we got exactly what we wanted.Packed in a cute take away box ,
not only the design but the flavour was also awesome.Loved the dark chocolate cupcakes .
will surely order more delicious cakes in future.
Worth trying for all your celebrations.
Thank you Madhuri for making amazing bachelorette themed cupcakes!! They were absolutely yummy 😋, soft and looked cute and tempting. The detailing on the cupcakes was perfect!!

Loved the cake, RedVelvet with chocolate icing and Surrounded by KitKat and surprise Gems inside.
The taste, the decoration and precision with minute details of the 🍰. Wonderfully presented.
Madhuri made this yummy Pokemon Greninja themed cake for my son's birthday.It was so colorful n very delicious.She was accessible on WhatsApp n Facebook..

Madhuri garu baked this beautiful cake even in a short notice! This layered chocolate cake was super tasty and not to forget the toppings which were beautifully carved.. she got some serious baking skills😊 thanks for making the moment special and a cakelicious one Madhuri garu

Recently ordered a cheese cake for my husbands birthday. Madhuri customized the cheesecake very well and added a surprise element to the cheesecake which was coffee liquor. The coffee liquor infused cheese cake was yummy and it was really very tasty.Also I ordered a eggless red velvet cheesecake which was also moist and tasty. Thank you so much madhuri for the excellent cake.
Recently I ordered red velvet cheese cake... The bread was very soft and the taste was really amazing... I will definitely recommend to order from Doughicious. :)

Madhuri made a birthday cake for my daughter, and it was delicious. It was a Ben and Holly cake, and she created the figures just as I wanted. She was always accessible on WhatsApp, and everything went smoothly. Thanks Madhuri.

I had ordered a black currant cheesecake for my friend's birthday! Alongside the yummy taste, the cheesecake was really well presented and well made! The owner is really kind and  accommodating by nature. Thanks again, we really enjoyed this experience and I recommend you to try the Ferrero Rocher cake as well.
Ordered a cake for my parent's wedding anniversary. Loved the cake so much. Everything was just perfect. The cake was very creamy. Just yummy!! Keep it up. Will surely visit again!!😍😊😊

@shrikanth thanks for the ferrero rocher and blackcurrant cheesecake ...it was one of best cakes i have tasted. It was top notch. The cheesecake was soft and it had a jelly top, which made it even more doughicious!!!

I ordered a Ferrero rocher cake for a birthday... The cake is home made and was exquisite.. The process of ordering the cake was pretty simple and straightforward. Now I went back for more... This time it is blackcurrent cheesecake... It was simple superb. The person who makes the cakes was very friendly. Payment is taken through paytm... So that's an advantage. People wanting a special cake for someone's birthday can definitely opt this.

Had ordered a fondant chocolate flavoured cake with lots of tiny details.The cake was rich, moist and absolutely delicious. 😊.All the details I had asked for had been included on the  cake. Excellent job Madhuri! :-).Keep up the good work!

It was an amazing service I got red velvet customised cupcakes. The cupcakes were really soft and tasted amazing with perfect icing at affordable price!! 
Impressed😁
ordered for customized cup cakes,and she made them exactly how i visualized in my mind.Suggested nice chocolate and caramel flavors with nuts. Thank you so much for memories....

Madhuri was just superb 👏 I could never thank her enough for doing this on such short notice and with such detailing. I ordered some gaming and animation character cupcakes for my boyfriend's birthday and she was so warm and full of ideas from the very beginning.
One can blindly go to her and be assured she'll deliver the best 😍

Recently got an opportunity to try their desserts. 
Chocolate cup cake was soft and had a moist centre, next was chocolate brownie this was definitely the best brownie I had till date crispy outside and gooey inside was just melt in mouth 😍. They also have dessert jars and cheese cakes, I tried their mango dessert jar and I just fell in love with it and the cheese cake too had a perfect texture and base was done perfectly too.
Give a try to have a doughicious experience.

Recently I tried their a box of goodies and it includes Blueberry cheesecake which was smooth and soft, bas was also good enough. Brownie was a two layered one which was lil spongy and crumbly had texture & small chocolate cupcake which was cute looking and tasted nice, and a jar of mango tiramisu which was really appetizing and had intense flavor!
Overall do worth of having anything.

I have tried cakes, brownies, biscuits all r damn good ...in cakes Madhuri does detailing work so nicely ..give her any design she will nail it ..she makes best items ..everyone should should try and it's worth it 🙂

For all the health conscious sweet loving people would definitely recommend DOUGHICIOUS for their wonderful cakes and brownies. Came across them through a reference and was very happy to know them as they perfectly matched my expectations. All the very best ......

Good pastries, tea time cakes and cookie we came across in recent days . Came across when searching for new joints in and around Gachibowli. Can be rated as one of the best home made goodies with quality ingredients

As we are looking for some organic cakes and bakes came across DOUGHICIOUS. They were making some good tea time cakes and brownies with best possible ingredients. Quality is top notch and are very happy to help with our needs. 
Wish them all the best and definitely recommend for people looking at organic bakes and cakes.

We were in search of a cake and that is when we landed up at Doughicious. We are very happy that we got to know them because they are one of the best in this trade with delicious and healthy cakes. The best part is they are all home made with no preservatives added. Definitely recommend people to try them out.
And wish them all the best
Yummy and deliciously home made bakes and cakes.. especially brownie and tea time cakes. They are definitely to be tried and recommend others to try...!!!

Amazing cakes! Excellent home-made customised baking . Totally reliable on quality and taste :) Can't resist once you have it!! The best home made cakes I hav ever tasted. They are sooo yummylicious.. Such a talented baker you are.... 😊😊

So glad we found "Doughicious". Not only was the cake exactly what we wanted - simple, delicious, good value - working with them was great. She was always very responsive. We went with the white forest cake with white chocolate cream filling and buttercream icing. It was perfect. I didn't want anything complicated and this worked perfectly. Definitely recommend.
Best brownies you can ever have. I can feel the exact same taste everytime I order. Worth trying it at least once. This is the best home baked food you can get.

My first 5 star rating in Zomato. 
Ordered pokemon themed cake. My kid, his friends and our guests loved it. 
Taste was awesome. Made our day with lovely memories.
One of the best fudge brownie you can find in the city. Also the pastries are too good to miss. Everything is home baked with good quality ingredients and care
